=======================
    Dermotology X Neural_Network
=======================

this is a Demo for a feature. it is meant to be used as an rest_API for every one who wish to get an analysis of any skin_condition. this is meant solely for giving the user the understanding if the skin condition shown in an image is one of the following condition:
1. fungus
2. melanoma
3. pimple
4. rush
5. nothing

a clear and correct diagnosis needs to be done by a proffessional in the relvant medical field. this is no more than a guide line and should be taken with a grain of salt.

Defnitions:

p = number of possible diagnosis for the input
k = number of frame retreive rom the video for diagnosis
x = name of diagnosis

diagnosis:
viral (Y/N)
fungial (Y/N)
rush (Y/N)

true 

arcitecture:
1. input from user 
2. if input is video:
    check for clear frames of the spot in need for diagnosis
    create a list of the k best frame for diagnosis (need to be an algorythm to getting the best frames)
3. run the inpiut through preproccessing.
4. send proccessed input to the NN for initial diagnosis. the first NN is for classifying the p possibilites for diagnosis 
5. send the input for the NN of the chosen diagnosis for more accurate result. 
6. return the diagnosis


DCNN models:

classifier : this DCNN's only purpose is to define narrow the ski disease to few realistic diagnosis. 
validate_X_diagnosis : X stands for the diangnosis. each diagnosis have it's own CNN that design to validate if it is said diagnosis or not. 